description.displayText: I have know Maranda since she was a child and have seen her grow into such a beautiful young lady. Maranda has been babysat for me for 5 years, she started with me when she was 10 and my kids absolutely loved. She's great with newborn she has this special touch to calm them down and put them to sleep. She's also great with other kids, she has so much energy and she's able to keep running around with kids until they go down.
